solution.p:
The requested set is described by .  It is easiest to find by using the procedure of .  Begin by row-reducing the matrix, viewing it as the coefficient matrix of a homogeneous system of equations.  We obtain\begin{bmatrix}
                \leading{1} & 0 & 1 & -2\\
