                0 & 0 & 0 & 0
                \end{bmatrix}.  Now build the vector form of the solutions to this homogeneous system ().  The free variables are x_3 and x_4, due to the locations of the non-pivot columns\colvector{x_1\\x_2\\x_3\\x_4}=
                x_3\colvector{-1\\-1\\1\\0}+
                x_4\colvector{2\\-1\\0\\1}.  The desired set S is simply the constant vectors in this expression, and these are the vectors \vect{z}_1 and \vect{z}_2 described by .S=\set{
                \colvector{-1\\-1\\1\\0},\,
                \colvector{2\\-1\\0\\1}
                }

